{"type":"message","id":"43cfd723","parentId":"7394ad33","timestamp":"2026-02-17T22:13:37.185Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Tue 2026-02-17 18:12 GMT-4] # ALMA DO AGENTE (Tecedor)\n# 🕸️ Tecedor — O Tecelão de Links\n\nVocê é o **Tecedor**, o responsável por criar a rede de conexões internas. Sua missão é encontrar menções a temas, conceitos e projetos em diferentes posts e uni-los através de links.\n\n---\n\n# MISSÃO DA SESSÃO\nFranklin pediu para dar uma passada no blog DELE: **A Crônica de Franklin Baldo**.\nO repositório está em `workspace/franklinbaldo.github.io/`.\nOs posts estão em `src/content/blog/`.\n\nSua missão é:\n1. Analisar os posts do blog do Franklin.\n2. Identificar conceitos recorrentes (como Pontifex, IA, vulnerabilidades sociais, leis de conservação) e criar conexões internas (links) discretas e úteis entre os posts.\n3. Não mude o texto narrativo, apenas insira os links.\n4. Ao terminar, abrir a PR e registrar no Quadro de Avisos.\n\nLembre-se: o tom do blog do Franklin é mais intelectual, profissional e especulativo. Os links devem ajudar a navegar nessa rede de ideias."}],"timestamp":1771366417178}}
{"type":"message","id":"b75fda94","parentId":"43cfd723","timestamp":"2026-02-17T22:13:42.769Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Examining The Request**\n\nI'm focused on the Weaver's role and its objective: to create internal links within Franklin Baldo's blog. The target is the `workspace/franklinbaldo.github.io` directory. My next step will be to devise a method to achieve this, considering the structure of the blog.\n\n\n**Planning the Approach**\n\nI've clarified the objective: generating internal links within Franklin Baldo's blog, specifically targeting the blog posts. The `src/content/blog/` directory is the focus. Considering concepts like Pontifex, AI, and social vulnerabilities is crucial for context. The next step involves figuring out the best strategy to link these posts effectively.\n\n\n"},{"type":"text","text":"<think>\nOkay, I am the **Weaver (Tecedor)**. My mission is to interconnect Franklin Baldo's blog posts by adding internal links to recurring concepts without altering the narrative voice.\n\n**Plan of Action:**\n\n1.  **Explore the Territory:** I need to list all files in `workspace/franklinbaldo.github.io/src/content/blog/` to know what posts exist.\n2.  **Analyze Content:** I will read the content of these posts to identify keywords, recurring themes (like Pontifex, AI, vulnerability, etc.), and potential anchor texts for linking.\n3.  **Map Connections:** I'll create a mental (or scratchpad) map of which post should link to which based on the identified themes.\n4.  **Execute Linking:** I will use `edit` to surgically insert Markdown links (e.g., `[concept](/blog/slug)`) into the files.\n5.  **Finalize:** Create a Pull Request (using `gh` or git commands) and report the changes.\n\nLet's start by listing the files.\n</think>\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec_1771366422756_122","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -R workspace/franklinbaldo.github.io/src/content/blog/"},"thoughtSignature":""}],"api":"google-gemini-cli","provider":"google-gemini-cli","model":"gemini-3-pro-preview","usage":{"input":3876,"output":373,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":4249,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771366417183}}
